{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8edbbbd1-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s288j"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"288j"},"text":"§ 288j.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" International Development Law Institute","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of the International Organizations Immunities Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s288"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 288","children":[],"tail":" and following), the International Development Law Institute shall be considered to be a public international organization in which the United States participates under the authority of an Act of Congress authorizing such participation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8edbbbd2-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/511/tVIII/s805"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–511, title VIII, § 805","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3353"},"text":"106 Stat. 3353","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8edbbbd3-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8edbbbd4-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id8edbbbd5-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The International Organizations Immunities Act, referred to in text, is title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1945-12-29/ch652"},"text":"act Dec. 29, 1945, ch. 652","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/59/669"},"text":"59 Stat. 669","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this subchapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s288"},"text":"section 288 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id8edbbbd6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Freedom for Russia and Emerging Eurasian Democracies and Open Markets Support Act of 1992, also known as the FREEDOM Support Act, and not as part of the International Organizations Immunities Act which comprises this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
